videos.description: Kyle Kuzma shuts down the Timberwolves on the fast break as he closes in on Anthony Edwards and blocks his layup attempt off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma swats Edwards' layup off the glass) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma swats Edwards' layup off the glass

videos.description: Alex Caruso weaves in the lane and puts up a smooth classic hook shot over the contest of Ed Davis for an impressive Lakers bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Caruso hits sweet, old-school hook shot over Davis) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caruso hits sweet, old-school hook shot over Davis

videos.description: LeBron James runs the fast break and drops a quick dime to Markieff Morris for the emphatic two-handed finish at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's smooth pass sets up Morris for dunk) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's smooth pass sets up Morris for dunk

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker comes up with a monster block, throwing Juancho Hernangomez's fast-break layup attempt off the bottom of the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Horton-Tucker chases down Hernangomez for big block) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Horton-Tucker chases down Hernangomez for big block

videos.description: LeBron James turns the ball over as he steps on a defender's foot and rolls his ankle, opening up the floor for Anthony Edwards to throw down a fast-break dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron rolls his ankle, Edwards throws down dunk) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron rolls his ankle, Edwards throws down dunk

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma throws yet another fancy pass as connects with Kentavious Caldwell-Pope around a defender for the big fast-break dunk for the Lakers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma's sweet dime sets up KCP for one-handed flush) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma's sweet dime sets up KCP for one-handed flush

videos.description: LeBron James goes deep in his bag and uses a variety of moves to shake Naz Reid and draw the contact as he finishes the and-1 layup on the baseline.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron works Reid on the baseline for and-1 bucket) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron works Reid on the baseline for and-1 bucket

videos.description: LeBron James gets the ball and throws a quick no-look pass to Marc Gasol who drains a 3 from the top of the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's no-look pass sets up Gasol for 3) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's no-look pass sets up Gasol for 3

videos.description: Marc Gasol drops a nice bounce pass through the crowded interior to a cutting LeBron James who takes flight to throw down a vicious dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gasol's bounce pass sets up LeBron for ferocious slam) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gasol's bounce pass sets up LeBron for ferocious slam

videos.description: The Lakers force the Timberwolves into a 24-second shot clock violation as Kyle Kuzma and Montrezl Harrell team up to get back-to-back blocks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma, Harrell force shot clock violation with back-to-back blocks) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma, Harrell force shot clock violation with back-to-back blocks

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma scores 20 points and racks up 3 blocked shots as he leads the Lakers to a 127-91 blowout win over the Timberwolves.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Kuzma leads the Lakers to decisive win over Timberwolves) 2020/12/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Kuzma leads the Lakers to decisive win over Timberwolves

videos.description: With Anthony Davis out, LeBron James scores 18 points and collects 9 rebounds and 5 assists as the Lakers take down the Timberwolves 127-91.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (LeBron puts on well-rounded performance vs. Timberwolves with no AD) 2020/12/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LeBron puts on well-rounded performance vs. Timberwolves with no AD
